wmmp3 - An mpg123 frontend designed for WindowMaker
				Munechika SUMIKAWA <sumikawa@kame.net>
				http://www.don.to/wmmp3/

wmmp3 is copyright (c) 1999-2000 by Munechika SUMIKAWA and licensed
through the GNU General Public License.  Read the COPYING file for the
complete GNU license.

--------------------------------------------------------------------
INSTALL:

1. install 'mpg123' at first. You can get it from 

2. tar zxvf wmmp3-0.2.tar.gz
   cd wmmp3-0.2
   ./configure
   xmkmf
   make
   su
   make install

--------------------------------------------------------------------
USAGE:

  1. make playlist on ~/.wmmp3

     e.g. mp3 files are installed on /usr/local/data/mp3
       % find /usr/local/data/mp3 -name '*.mp3' > ~/.wmmp3

     NOTE: All filenames are designated as a ABSOLUTELY path.
           You can also designate URL in ~/.wmmp3, such as
	   http://foo.bar.baz:8000/

  2. execute wmmp3
       % wmmp3

  3. enjoy!

